```console
kettle-jem
bundle exec rake kettle:jem:install
bundle exec rake kettle:jem:selftest
```

`kettle-jem` setup creates or updates `.kettle-jem.yml`, installs template
support, and runs the template workflow. `kettle:jem:install` reapplies
template updates. `kettle:jem:selftest` checks template drift in a temporary
workspace.
